{"tid":1233453,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【注意！注意！】準備好捨身衝擊嘅人入嚟睇下先（好重要）","createTime":"2019-06-16T18:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T19:42:06.000Z","uid":191462,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c10bb5318cbe115fc1513f267d37a22ccfb0c186","tid":1233453,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:51:55.000Z","msg":"如果你在場有朋友喺到俾人水咗去下齊準備衝擊物資<br />\n麻煩你提醒佢哋已經犯梗刑毀<br />\n隨時在場義士都準備俾佢哋累埋非法集會<br />\n班<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府軍</span></span>又準備出師有名<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果佢哋準備衝擊警方同建築物<br />\n叫佢哋走遠啲 唔好走入和理非入面衝擊警察 <br />\n唔好要在場人士同你一齊喺到𠄘擔風險 <br />\n其實咁樣做好自私好蠢 亦都危害梗在場集會人士<br />\n你哋衝擊嘅想法 可能係會達到一定效果<br />\n<br />\n不過係衝之前 可以諗下點樣<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">達到效果之餘又唔會累到自己人 </span></span> <br />\n<br />\n因為在場冇一個人應該要為你哋嘅行為流血同拎條命嚟搏 你哋自己都知啲警察已經係癲咗 我真係唔想再見到有自己人<span style=\"color: red;\">受傷</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">死</span>"},{"pid":"e6fe57ea21f294455ddae302d7b24f0289ef3258","tid":1233453,"uid":143210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c10bb5318cbe115fc1513f267d37a22ccfb0c186","tid":1233453,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:51:55.000Z","msg":"如果你在場有朋友喺到俾人水咗去下齊準備衝擊物資<br />\n麻煩你提醒佢哋已經犯梗刑毀<br />\n隨時在場義士都準備俾佢哋累埋非法集會<br />\n班<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府軍</span></span>又準備出師有名<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果佢哋準備衝擊警方同建築物<br />\n叫佢哋走遠啲 唔好走入和理非入面衝擊警察 <br />\n唔好要在場人士同你一齊喺到𠄘擔風險 <br />\n其實咁樣做好自私好蠢 亦都危害梗在場集會人士<br />\n你哋衝擊嘅想法 可能係會達到一定效果<br />\n<br />\n不過係衝之前 可以諗下點樣<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">達到效果之餘又唔會累到自己人 </span></span> <br />\n<br />\n因為在場冇一個人應該要為你哋嘅行為流血同拎條命嚟搏 你哋自己都知啲警察已經係癲咗 我真係唔想再見到有自己人<span style=\"color: red;\">受傷</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">死</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:52:54.000Z","msg":"而家係和理非嘅回合！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唱歌嘅時候就係夜晚<br />\n<br />\n衝嘅時候就係日頭"},{"pid":"b9ab5cbc1b8c56bf3fdc968975cb39ac99d720b0","tid":1233453,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:54:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0584ae94690c9e253e1168ca7b410fc9b0f47f","tid":1233453,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:55:01.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33fd117b2a2520d78aa56c188405e434f42985b","tid":1233453,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:55:20.000Z","msg":"推多次 因為好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc0f3efe1079540b780574a6cbf6b9ec1ecd873","tid":1233453,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:07:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aceb40ac6b3deee5d9c3e4d67c3897a8345de2a0","tid":1233453,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:07:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9fe019f383c78976db84913b53963fe2c69ae7d8","tid":1233453,"uid":225531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:08:02.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n有去發夢嘅年輕人，可能你就快18歲、啱18歲，又或者係過歲數但未登記成為選民，可唔可以用少少時間填吓選民登記，收保皇黨香港走狗嘅皮，投番啲正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（你有兩票，一票自己住嗰區，另一票係超級區議會，好好善用佢）<br />\n<br />\n地方選區：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/main.jsp?rt=GC&amp;applicationId=GC1&amp;module=1&amp;language=zh&amp;country=HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2Fra008%2Fmain.jsp%3Frt%3DGC%26applicationId%3DGC1%26module%3D1%26language%3Dzh%26country%3DHK&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4bZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=265ff000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/main.jsp?rt=GC&amp;applicationId=GC1&amp;module=1&amp;language=zh&amp;country=HK</a><br />\n<br />\n功能組別&mdash; 區議會（第二）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/main.jsp?rt=FC&amp;applicationId=FC41&amp;module=41&amp;language=zh&amp;country=HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2Fra008%2Fmain.jsp%3Frt%3DFC%26applicationId%3DFC41%26module%3D41%26language%3Dzh%26country%3DHK&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4bZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=b880d083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/main.jsp?rt=FC&amp;applicationId=FC41&amp;module=41&amp;language=zh&amp;country=HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n屋企人阻住你發夢嘅香港人，可唔可以幫下文宣組手足，簽吓聯署、整圖、share post咁，多一個係一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【 突發】正式開火！第一批信已發出！我地香港人要幫政府官員、保皇黨取消外國護照！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【 突發】第二輪炮火！行動升級！除咗取消港共外國護照，我地正式開辟聯合國人道罪行戰線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1217474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1217474</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【 突發】第三波強攻！不撤不散！林鄭月娥、速龍指揮、江敏強，我地要你地生生世世被困大灣區！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1226922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1226922</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n投柒訴CCTVB<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4bZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=1ffb91de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n「TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實」<br />\n<br />\n時間12-17/6/2019 任何一日，任何一段新聞報導，6:00am 得、6:30pm 又得<br />\n81台，83台有得<br />\n「呃我老母屌你老母」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4bZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=1ffb91de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n<br />\n好叻叫醒裝睡的人嘅香港人，可唔可以再幫幫手炮轟佢地，用理據，一巴巴摑醒仍在裝睡嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（對唔住我口才唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 交俾咁多位巴絲freestyle）"},{"pid":"20a7076fabbf8e7788537f23b7f8fc5fba86b951","tid":1233453,"uid":236878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:08:35.000Z","msg":"依家唔好衝啊 冷靜啊 <br />\n行足一日 攰啦 <br />\n今日唔多覺見到警察 佢哋分分鐘全日涼住冷氣以逸待勞啊 <br />\n你玩total war都唔會用疲勞民兵打精力充沛精兵掛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要衝 可以 不過等我們休息同準備充足 出師有名 我哋先一齊衝 好唔好?</span>"},{"pid":"c1c274d57b2605c65ae3eb23cf7f6720963052c5","tid":1233453,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"唔衝得唔準備得流血或者死就躝返屋企，咪撚喺到指指點點，而家係Die for HK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f32c79d7d8f87dd920609983c4436ab0967d2cc","tid":1233453,"uid":191462,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1c274d57b2605c65ae3eb23cf7f6720963052c5","tid":1233453,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":2,"scor